{"tid":2495607,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：北韓禁白票 香港只差一線（李八方）","createTime":"2021-04-19T09:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T09:37:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2b53ffa55326579a59c759b9b915b61f47a80a83","tid":2495607,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:34:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/2G5PKFTLS5GBZNNZ55Z5G6DVTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2F2G5PKFTLS5GBZNNZ55Z5G6DVTE%2F&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx6NFN85aI5NoQ2W41nR4Hcs%3D&h=148cbeda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210419%2F2G5PKFTLS5GBZNNZ55Z5G6DVTE%2F&h=0f646797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210419/2G5PKFTLS5GBZNNZ55Z5G6DVTE/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：北韓禁白票 香港只差一線（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3WZYqQVB6W0et4wqOzApIof140c=/510x417/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SRPYCGOYPNHYNJH5RYPWOGM4TA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3WZYqQVB6W0et4wqOzApIof140c%3D%2F510x417%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSRPYCGOYPNHYNJH5RYPWOGM4TA.jpg&h=2f01b6bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港府之前公佈「完善」香港選舉嘅條例草案，入面引入呼籲人投白票、唔投票都係犯法嘅新規定，但又話選民投白票唔係犯法，好多政界人士、學者、大狀都問，點解叫人做唔係犯法嘅嘢會變咗犯法？佢哋同時話冇聽過外國選舉法有啲咁嘅規定，唔知係咪香港先有呢啲限制，但有facebook專頁發現，原來唔係只得香港話呼籲人投白票犯法，真係有個國家投白票都犯法，呢個國家係邊度？原來係北韓！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n投廢票當叛國<br />\n<br />\nFB專頁Goodbye HK, Hello UK引述兩篇分別係《經濟學人》同BBC有關北韓選舉制度嘅報道，原來北韓選區每區只有一個候選人，全部候選人由執政勞動黨之下嘅祖國統一聯盟挑選，而選舉日全國17歲以上嘅人士必須到票站投票以示愛國，因為候選人只得一個，選票上只有一個格仔，任何人投白票或廢票都當叛國。北韓選民都可以投反對嘅，不過要當眾將選票投入另一個票箱，即係全部人都見到投反對票。<br />\n<br />\n專頁又引述報道，北韓2019年選舉嘅投票率去到99.7%，完全係民主選舉嘅「典範」，香港竟然可以係投票規範上直追北韓，真係難得！<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"3bd62ca15fb4c8e4e2183a55f7dc2ff4a394b525","tid":2495607,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T09:37:33.000Z","msg":"中國都冇白票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmT1xLPX1oWWuGFCGspT9dCrpKmb2QzigWeuW3XS7xT5GQ?filename=SxjFOAr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSxjFOAr.jpg&h=5a967f36&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}